{"tid":288372,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"其實宜家仲有冇DSE雞係純理","createTime":"2017-06-18T06:48:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-22T14:44:35.000Z","uid":35136,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5f8f15500d00c629cbfe162eeee67bba509fb909","tid":288372,"uid":35136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T06:48:49.000Z","msg":"入到大學先發現好多同窗嘅母校係分班上唔俾佢哋揀齊phy chem bio  一定要理搭科商或者ict又冇乜人讀過m1m2 好多人淨讀兩個x<br />\n但科學phy chem bio math環環緊扣<br />\n上到大學讀純理冇個底 唔覺得好反智咩<br />\n仲多唔多人係讀齊phy chem bio m1/m2<br />\n有冇人淨係讀咗一兩個理科X上到大學讀純理分享下<br />\n利申:14年DSEphy chem bio m2"},{"pid":"b9b85bc9b72706fb099345a59e51460b4b565a1f","tid":288372,"uid":36287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T06:50:21.000Z","msg":"其實唔少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但好多未必大學揀pure sci"},{"pid":"3e7e173fa0e1858c52dbb70a92242546e5c6dbdf","tid":288372,"uid":41742,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T06:54:51.000Z","msg":"大部分人都係2 electives<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d9599a0f3c85674f8a3a2772b8fcb320f4a6d77","tid":288372,"uid":76514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T06:58:32.000Z","msg":"phy chem bio M2<br />\n一科都無drop讀到考DSE<br />\n依家大學讀science<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82e35cc821e6b24576f7386f3482afeb8829a86b","tid":288372,"uid":76514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T07:00:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>phy chem bio M2<br />\n一科都無drop讀到考DSE<br />\n依家大學讀science<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n未打完<br />\n讀到大學真係覺得啲無讀純理既人追得好辛苦<br />\nfoundation course咩都有啲<br />\n但無其中一科底既人就咁上堂根本咩都聽唔明"},{"pid":"15960e50cd68d262ba8a1441e97ff2740e575261","tid":288372,"uid":35136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T07:03:34.000Z","msg":"其實點解有啲中學唔俾人讀phy chem bio<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0652382b645dcb8dc6e37283789d1f94eae8037b","tid":288372,"uid":113465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T07:06:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實點解有啲中學唔俾人讀phy chem bio<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n通常睇你中三個科既排名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eb3fdcb3b0a8469eb0af07edfb7562aefcd3104","tid":288372,"uid":35136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T07:09:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>phy chem bio M2<br />\n一科都無drop讀到考DSE<br />\n依家大學讀science<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n未打完<br />\n讀到大學真係覺得啲無讀純理既人追得好辛苦<br />\nfoundation course咩都有啲<br />\n但無其中一科底既人就咁上堂根本咩都聽唔明</blockquote><br />\n我都覺 一個sem要補人哋讀三年嘅底<br />\n新高中變相要人中三揀科個時決定晒前程"},{"pid":"15164503c18e5cb5bb3d0c883c5461198e40050f","tid":288372,"uid":3935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T07:27:27.000Z","msg":"講真, 好多人係初中唔夠料先會比人limit 左去2x, 咁怪得邊個<br />\n另外, 我同你同屆既, 我地果時就話m2當半科可以攝埋m1 2 黎讀姐,<br />\n但係後我地一兩屆開始m1 2 根本都當左做一科啦. 咁又點會有咁多學校比人讀8x, 前提係你入u 都剩係睇5/6 科"},{"pid":"0bf7a9bf0d931400e8ca9d4a547f5ff53e930a82","tid":288372,"uid":69289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T08:18:02.000Z","msg":"好多engine同學同我講冇讀過phy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外都好多冇傳統理科底，95% 2X 仲要係得一個X係理科"},{"pid":"538ede121149cd28c7800d343d80e2da0e2096b6","tid":288372,"uid":69289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T08:31:18.000Z","msg":"根本教育局就on9<br />\n<br />\nm1 m2 自己衝出黎柒同人講話當半科計，點知間間大學理鳩佢當一科咁計分，好心加課程獨立左佢啦屌老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\ncombine science又係推學生去死，深度會考都不如，但量又唔係少，想抄舊制整個ASL Subject出黎又唔用下個腦，舊制學生本身有CE full subject底，上到AL揀ASL就真係讀「真」半科野，但DSE呢？基本既課程 &quot;CE&quot; 都學唔足，就夾硬加埋另一science suject做所謂一科，量係多喇，害撚死班學生，個qualification 實質都唔知叫CE定DSE好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"959823bff5fc7f53e98e0835104e5da1b48bcf92","tid":288372,"uid":120051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T09:50:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根本教育局就on9<br />\n<br />\nm1 m2 自己衝出黎柒同人講話當半科計，點知間間大學理鳩佢當一科咁計分，好心加課程獨立左佢啦屌老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\ncombine science又係推學生去死，深度會考都不如，但量又唔係少，想抄舊制整個ASL Subject出黎又唔用下個腦，舊制學生本身有CE full subject底，上到AL揀ASL就真係讀「真」半科野，但DSE呢？基本既課程 &quot;CE&quot; 都學唔足，就夾硬加埋另一science suject做所謂一科，量係多喇，害撚死班學生，個qualification 實質都唔知叫CE定DSE好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1add38111a33857f5f89507a17effa15b8138cbf","tid":288372,"uid":104360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T10:39:03.000Z","msg":"只讀phy chem路過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實好多學校都分哂組指定你讀邊科 根本唔到你揀<br />\n而且好多學校唔開3X 原因係上堂會好麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0f2c1a89f9b2ebecb6f7800c7581bd63f46775d","tid":288372,"uid":35136,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T13:46:23.000Z","msg":"其實最on9真係m1m2 當半個x 我間中學冇上堂時間冇堂教 要一星期一